    public interface IGeneObjSurf
extends IGeneObj
    Interface describing the requirements for surfacic geographic objects handled by the different generalisation modules of CartAGen. Other interfaces extend this one, based on the geographical thematic of the objects. The objects handled within CartAGen belong to classes that implement these more specific interfaces.
    Author:
    Cecile Duchene, IGN-F, COGIT Lab.
